{
  "stem": "21582.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They won't kill me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[CRYING] And my father said, child, [SOBBING] don't do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[CRYING] Maybe that's how-- maybe that was a spark of will that he gave me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But he also gave me that cyanide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But things was so terrible that my, my, my relief at the moment was-- that I have the escape because I'm going to poison myself.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they won't get me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Well, my father was-- that was the last we saw of our father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The next time that we had any any sort of communication about our father was quite a bit later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "When we were taken in behind the barbed wires, and we were in the barracks, and we were sent to do forced labor-- that my sister once was marching with a-- with a group.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she saw from the distance, not too far passing, a, a, a, a group of men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she recognized something-- someone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, oh, where is my father?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, look, see that wagon over there, the truck.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a truck smoldering with bones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, your father is there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the last we-- or, you know, the last communication.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we knew that our father would be the least likely to survive because he was already so-- in such poor physical health.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But nevertheless, [LAUGHS] my sister was still hoping.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After, after coming back to the field and coming back to where my father was separated with a man on that field across from us, the next thing I remember is taking through the showers.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, that, too, was a petrifying experience, because we knew of the showers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we knew that, in most cases, what came out of the shower was, was the gas.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
